    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、こんばんは！\n大晦日にライブに来てくれて、ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.599999102,
      "endTime": 12.7375049193,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.9308382909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "今年の締めくくり、そして来年も最高の一年となるよう\nみんなで、お祝いしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9308382909,
      "endTime": 19.5954413334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "そして、みんなももう知ってると思うけど\nⅢXの公式チャンネルが、今日オープンしました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8087744951,
      "endTime": 28.4424937487,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3100.0000477
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.6291603009
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "このライブも、全世界に生配信中です！\nネットで応援してくれてるみんなも、ありがと～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6291603009,
      "endTime": 36.0691601674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2558267196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "新曲情報から、このチャンネルでしか見られない\n私達のオフまで、どんどん配信する予定です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2558267196,
      "endTime": 42.9467359146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "kana、こっちでも金の盾ほしいんで！！\n絶対、チャンネル登録してね～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1334024669,
      "endTime": 48.840068745800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.1334024669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、少しだけ気が早いですが\n一年の始まりをイメージした曲をお送りします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.0267355842,
      "endTime": 55.626735775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8134026132
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "来年も、いい年になることを願って\nそれでは、『Inside Out』――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8134026132,
      "endTime": 63.2999998729,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1966.6650452999975
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 64.531177672
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、終わった終わった\nったく、あんた達の顔を見ながら年越しとかさぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.581177672,
      "endTime": 73.21530462129999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6850.980186400008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 73.4153045259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、{user}さんからメール",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4153045259,
      "endTime": 75.5598833325,
      "sfxList": [
