    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "チャンネルの登録者数、初動で三十万だってさ\nこれって、いい数字なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3335649731,
      "endTime": 82.9267621281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 83.1400955758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "国内基準なら、まあまあかな\nでもまだkanaのチャンネルには、全然負けるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1400955758,
      "endTime": 90.0451747499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 90.2318415882
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、kanaのチャンネルは海外からも見られてるし\nそうなると、数字が桁から違うからさ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2318415882,
      "endTime": 99.1183493854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、とにかくこれで肩の荷が下りたわ\n正月は、やっとゆっくり休めそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3316827378,
      "endTime": 105.906490191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 99.3316827378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ライブとチャンネルの準備で、全然休む暇なかったしね\nもう正月はゴロゴロする、全力でゴロゴロしてやるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1198236388,
      "endTime": 116.2114791793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 106.1198236388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "貴方はまず、今からでも大掃除をしなさい\nさて……それじゃあ、私は先に帰らせてもらうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4181457124,
      "endTime": 125.20510707700001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 125.3984401625
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "それと……儀礼として、一応言っておくけれど\n二人とも、あけましておめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3984401625,
      "endTime": 133.6924086492,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9201.565559600012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 133.8857420207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい。あけましておめでとう\n……あれ？　なんで私の部屋のこと知ってるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8857420207,
      "endTime": 143.2719324351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 137.6333399139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――1月1日、午後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1452647132,
      "endTime": 145.2452647132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.311935751
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 145.3452581011
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 145.4666722301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、ただの街中の神社だと思ってたけど\nさすがに元旦ともなると、そこそこ人がいるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.1452581011,
      "endTime": 155.361765822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.5484323743
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "ま、お参りだけしてさっさと帰ろ……\n…………げ。なんでいるのよ、あんた達",
